title: Chanel CC Straw Tote Bag
description: Chanel CC straw tote bag in pink woven raffia and with leather trims (#10xxxxxx: 2005-2006). Featuring matt gold-toned hardware, dual leather-chain woven shoulder straps and a fold over leather strap with classic CC turn-lock closure. This opens to a pink logo printed nylon lining 2 compartment divided by a centre zipper pocket. Approx. dimensions: 37cm(Top-L) x 21cm(H) x 14cm(D) and 20cm shoulder strap drop. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
